'''Anarrad''' was the name given to a pit located on the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]]. Infested with [[Katarn/Legends|katarns]], it provided an ideal place for young Wookiees to prove themselves or for others to keep sharp in their [[Hunting/Legends|hunting]] skills. [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] went hunting there at least five times in his life.<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos I: Hero's Trial">''[[The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos I: Hero's Trial]]''</ref>

